t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_0::go: Yeroo qaamichi adeemsicha jalqabuuf qophaa'utti waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_3::go: Tarkaanfii adeemsichaa barbaachisaa itti aanurratti qaamicha waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_7::go: Seenicha xumuri, akka inni itti xumure nutti himi.
t_process_profile_audio::text_card_1::te: Sagalee gosa garagaraa waraabi - qaamicha ibsa kennu, sagalee jijjiirama yookaan tarkaanfii addaa adeemsichaa agarsiisu.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_2::go: Sagalee bakka adeemsichi itti ta'aa jiruu waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_5::go: Yoo adeemsichi hordoftoota qabaate, gocha deebiisaanii waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::text_card_0::te: Sagalee adeemsicha cimsuuf barbaachisurratti xiyyeeffadhu. Kan si barbaachisu hundasaa miti, tarkaanfileen adeemsasaa jalqabarraa hanga xumuraatti agarsiisan ga'oodha.
t_process_profile_audio::title: Adeemsa odeeffannoo Dhuunfaa
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_4::go: Sagalee hordoftootatti waan ta'aa jiru himu waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_1::go: Jalqaba adeemsichaa yookaan tarkaanfii jalqabaa adeemsichaa waraabi.
t_process_profile_audio::clip_card_6::go: Yeroo qaamichi adeemsicha itti xumuru waraabi.
